  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/955591fc4f00dc02668da8ff278508e5.poster.avif?t=1755116858\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/955591fc4f00dc02668da8ff278508e5.webm?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/955591fc4f00dc02668da8ff278508e5.mp4?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JUMP INTO THE CHAOS – PLAY FOR FREE! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your friends and dive into the ultimate multiplayer party battle royale! Race, stumble, and battle it out in hilarious obstacle courses where only one player can become the winner - will it be you? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>32-PLAYER MULTIPLAYER ONLINE MADNESS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against up to 32 players in fast-paced, chaotic matches and tournaments. Can you dodge, jump, and stumble your way to victory?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/21c1dff8383138f8c13de07b4e9a4da1.poster.avif?t=1755116858\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/21c1dff8383138f8c13de07b4e9a4da1.webm?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/21c1dff8383138f8c13de07b4e9a4da1.mp4?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAY TOURNAMENTS & CLIMB THE RANKED LEADERBOARD </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, clash, kick and fall to survive in tournaments and collect points to climb the Ranked leaderboard and unlock cool rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>60+ COOL MAPS, ENDLESS FUN!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed through insane obstacle courses, dodge crazy traps, and outplay your rivals! With over 60 maps packed with challenges, every match is a new adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZE YOUR STUMBLER – THOUSANDS OF COSMETICS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock epic skins, hilarious emotes, and more to stand out from the crowd. Become a ninja, superhero, or even a chicken, there’s a style for everyone. Collect them all and show them off!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/12daac30d542a385761fb236ff2c99d1.poster.avif?t=1755116858\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/12daac30d542a385761fb236ff2c99d1.webm?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/12daac30d542a385761fb236ff2c99d1.mp4?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LIMITED-TIME EVENTS & AWESOME CROSSOVERS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into special events playing the best game modes like Floor is Lava and Banana Bonanza or expand your collection with legendary stumblers from SpongeBob, My Hero Academia, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CROSS-PLAY ON STEAM & MOBILE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play anywhere, anytime! Stumble Guys is free to play and supports cross-play between Steam and mobile, so you can battle your friends no matter where they are!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready to stumble? Download now and join the fun!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/955591fc4f00dc02668da8ff278508e5.poster.avif?t=1755116858\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/955591fc4f00dc02668da8ff278508e5.webm?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/955591fc4f00dc02668da8ff278508e5.mp4?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JUMP INTO THE CHAOS – PLAY FOR FREE! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your friends and dive into the ultimate multiplayer party battle royale! Race, stumble, and battle it out in hilarious obstacle courses where only one player can become the winner - will it be you? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>32-PLAYER MULTIPLAYER ONLINE MADNESS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against up to 32 players in fast-paced, chaotic matches and tournaments. Can you dodge, jump, and stumble your way to victory?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/21c1dff8383138f8c13de07b4e9a4da1.poster.avif?t=1755116858\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/21c1dff8383138f8c13de07b4e9a4da1.webm?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/21c1dff8383138f8c13de07b4e9a4da1.mp4?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAY TOURNAMENTS & CLIMB THE RANKED LEADERBOARD </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, clash, kick and fall to survive in tournaments and collect points to climb the Ranked leaderboard and unlock cool rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>60+ COOL MAPS, ENDLESS FUN!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed through insane obstacle courses, dodge crazy traps, and outplay your rivals! With over 60 maps packed with challenges, every match is a new adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZE YOUR STUMBLER – THOUSANDS OF COSMETICS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock epic skins, hilarious emotes, and more to stand out from the crowd. Become a ninja, superhero, or even a chicken, there’s a style for everyone. Collect them all and show them off!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/12daac30d542a385761fb236ff2c99d1.poster.avif?t=1755116858\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/12daac30d542a385761fb236ff2c99d1.webm?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677740/extras/12daac30d542a385761fb236ff2c99d1.mp4?t=1755116858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LIMITED-TIME EVENTS & AWESOME CROSSOVERS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into special events playing the best game modes like Floor is Lava and Banana Bonanza or expand your collection with legendary stumblers from SpongeBob, My Hero Academia, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CROSS-PLAY ON STEAM & MOBILE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play anywhere, anytime! Stumble Guys is free to play and supports cross-play between Steam and mobile, so you can battle your friends no matter where they are!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready to stumble? Download now and join the fun!</strong></p>",
